“aim_ogc_deagle”

As per request, I have made the second official map for an online aim competition in New Zealand, called "aim_ogc_deagle", for "OGC NZ" Online Gaming Competition (www.ogc.net.nz).

This map was designed for an OGC 2v2 Deagle, single elimination tournament.

- 24 Spawn points, 12 per team
- There are 6 extra Deagles on the ground for each team.
- Each player also starts with a Deagle pistol and knife.
- No Buy Zones
- Contains an overview radar
- Nav File for bots
- Optimized with No Draw for better FPS
- All files compiled into the .bsp using Pakrat

Blair (Bobpoblo) Burkhardt - Level Design
http://www.fpsbanana.com/members/776402
